# Ecart Pay documentation first

When building or debugging an Ecart Pay integration:

1. Start from the agent index: https://docs.ecartpay.com/llms.txt
2. Open the matching guide or API reference page before writing code.
3. Prefer the `ecartpay` MCP server (`https://ecartpay.readme.io/mcp`) for docs search when available.
4. Never invent endpoints, request fields, response shapes, webhook event names, or status values.
5. Prefer sandbox hosts and keys while implementing: `https://sandbox.ecartpay.com`.
6. Cite the docs URL you used when explaining an API decision.
